 Host Privacy Policy\">Privacy Policy</a>). They accept PayPal.</p><p><b>Here\u2019s a little about The Venus Host in their own words:</b></p><p><em>We are India Based Domain Registration And Website Hosting Service Provider.&nbsp; We provide Domain Registration services for more more than 100 TLDs And Website Hosting Service across Linux, Windows And WordPress Hosting Platforms.&nbsp; Our Specialty is we activate the order immediately after the successful payment.</em></p><p>Have you been a The Venus Host customer? Please share your experience in the comments below.</p><p><b>Now read more to see the offer!</b></p><p><span id=\"more-27729\"></span></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Pandemic Relaxation Offer</b></p><ul><li>Free SSL Certificate</li><li>Free Global CDN</li><li>Free DDoS Protection</li><li>Free Website Builder</li><li>Unmetered Bandwidth</li><li>2 GB X 10 Email Addresses</li><li>1 GB X 2 MySQL Databases</li><li>[<a href=\"https://thevenushost.com/index.php?rp=/store/special-plans\" aria-label=\"The Venus Host Offer Order Link\">ORDER</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><div></div><div>Please let us know if you have any questions/comments and enjoy!</div><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lowendboxtv-weekend-update-for-july-3-2021/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"LowEndBoxTV Weekend Update for July 3, 2021\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/leb-wu-20210703-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #3333